OL,3,CReform UK councillor resigns less than
OL,4,Ctwo weeks after being elected
OL,6,FA Reform UK councillor has resigned
OL,7,Fless than two weeks after being
OL,8,Felected.
OL,10,FDanielle Cavanagh was elected to
OL,11,Frepresent the High Fell Ward in
OL,12,FGateshead in the elections held on 7
OL,13,FMay.
OL,15,FHowever, the party have now confirmed
OL,16,Fshe has already stepped down due to a
OL,17,F"significant expansion of her business
OL,18,Fcommitments" during the final weeks of
OL,19,Fthe campaign.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
