OL,3,CReform UK councillor resigns less than
OL,4,Ctwo weeks after being elected
OL,6,FIn a letter to High Fell residents,
OL,7,FReform chair in Gateshead and Whickham
OL,8,FLindsay Atkinson wrote: "It is with
OL,9,Fgreat regret that I write to formally
OL,10,Finform you that one of our
OL,11,Fcouncillors, Danielle Cavanagh, has
OL,12,Fdecided to step down from her position
OL,13,Fas your local councillor.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
