CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1779466274
OL,3,CReform UK councillor resigns less than
OL,4,Ctwo weeks after being elected
OL,6,F"Firstly, Danielle would like to
OL,7,Fexpress her sincere gratitude to
OL,8,Feveryone who placed their trust and
OL,9,Fconfidence in her during the election
OL,10,Fcampaign. It was a genuine privilege
OL,11,Ffor her to be chosen to represent the
OL,12,FHigh Fell community and to be elected
OL,13,Fby the residents of High Fell.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1779466274
OL,3,CReform UK councillor resigns less than
OL,4,Ctwo weeks after being elected
OL,6,F"Unexpectedly, during the latter
OL,7,Fstages of the campaign process leading
OL,8,Fup to Danielle's successful election,
OL,9,Fher business commitments have expanded
OL,10,Fsignificantly. What began as a
OL,11,Fbusiness operating primarily in the
OL,12,FNorth East has now grown across the
OL,13,FSouth of England, requiring far more
OL,14,Fof her time, travel, and day-to-day
OL,15,Finvolvement than she had anticipated,
OL,16,Fwhich now includes further college
OL,17,Ftraining.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1779466274
OL,3,CReform UK councillor resigns less than
OL,4,Ctwo weeks after being elected
OL,6,F"As a result of the above, and after
OL,7,Fcareful consideration, Danielle has
OL,8,Fcome to the difficult decision that
OL,9,Fshe wouldn't be able to dedicate the
OL,10,Flevel of time, energy, and commitment
OL,11,Fthat the role of councillor rightly
OL,12,Fdeserves."
OL,14,FShe added that Ms Cavanagh "sincerely
OL,15,Fapologised" for the decision, which
OL,16,Fwas "not taken lightly."
OL,18,FReform have vowed to contest the by-
OL,19,Felection which will now take place
OL,20,Fwith a new candidate.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
